Branch: 
"**Any reference with a decision**&D" ; **Any json access to a field.-ß>** ˇ **Any json access to a field.-ß>** : Execute the command in the specified field and continue main execution from there
"**Any reference with a decision**&D" ; **Any json access to a field.-ß|** ˇ **Any json access to a field.-ß|** : Execute the command in the specified field and continue main execution from the invoker step
"**Any reference with a decision**&D" ; **Any json access to a field.-ß<** ˇ **Any json access to a field.-ß<** : Execute the command in the specified field and start main execution from the first step until it reaches there
"**Any reference with a decision**&D" ; **Any json access to a field.-ß** ˇ **Any json access to a field.-ß<** : Execute the command in the specified field and start main execution from the begining
Loop:
**Any json access to a command**.-@> : Execute all the functions with all the commands in the step and continue main execution from there
**Any json access to a command**.-@| : Execute all the functions with all the commands in the step and continue main execution from the invoker step
**Any json access to a command**.-@< : Execute all the functions with all the commands in the step and start main execution from the first step until it reaches there
**Any json access to a command**.-@ : Execute all the functions with all the commands in the step and start main execution from the begining
#The execution of commands happen from top to down specified in the document
